  title `Page 12`
  content obj_root_law_sections_12_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_12_footnotes
  sourcePage 12
obj_root_law_sections_12_content:
  string
  line 12
  line `called or known as the Sibtainabad Emambarra and secondly all that small building or mosque together`
  line `with the piece or parcel of land on which the same is erected and built and the approach way thereto in the`
  line `said Sched ule hereto secondly more particularly described together with all out - buildings and out - offices`
  line `and all ways, paths, passages, railings, tanks, waters, water - courses, drains, rights, easements and`
  line `appurtenances to the said premises respectively belonging o r in anywise appertaining or therewith held used`
  line `or enjoyed and all the estate right title and interest of the Agent and of the estate of the said Wajid Ali Shah`
  line `King of Oudh into and upon the premises T O HAVE AND TO HOLD the said Emambarra and mosque piec es`
  line `or parcels of land and other the hereditaments and premises hereinbefore expressed to be hereby assured`
  line `with the appurtenances unto and to the use of the said parties of the second part their executors`
  line `administrators and assigns and assigns as joint ten ants and not as tenants in common upon the trust declared`
  line `of and concerning the same in and by the Wakfnamah or declaration of trust hereinbefore referred to and`
  line `intended to be executed by them of even date with these presents. And the Agent enters into no covenants`
  line `for title.`
  line ________
  line `The S chedule above referred to.`
  line `P ART I.`
  line `All the Emambarra or building together with the piece or parcel of land on which the same is erected`
  line `and built situate and being at Garden Reach on the south side of the Garden R each in the Registration`
  line `District of the 24 - Pergunnahs Sub - district of Alipore and Thana of Sonai Bazar containing an area of 1`
  line `bigha 9 cottahs 7 chittacks or thereabouts and bound on the north by Garden Reach Road on the south by`
  line `land belonging to the Bho okoilas Raj estate on the east partly by the premises of the late Nawab Yadyar`
  line `Mehal Sahiba and partly by a piece of land belonging to the Estate of the late Prince Mirza Mahomed Jogee`
  line `Bahadur and on the west by an old building said to be the property of o ne Rais Hyder and formerly known`
  line `as the house of the late Zulfikurud - Dowlah.`
  line `P ART II.`
  line `All that small mosque or building together with the piece or parcel of land whereon the same is erected`
  line `and built situate within the ground of the premises known as the Shah Munzil belonging to the estate of the`
  line `late Prince Sir Jehan Kader Mirza at Garden Reach in the Registration District, Sub - district and Thana`
  line `aforesaid and bounded on the north by the Court - yard of the Sahah Munzil, on the south partly by the`
  line `private r oad leading from the Shah Munzil to the Sultan Bazar Road and partly by a tank, on the east by`
  line `Iron Gates belonging to the Shah Munzil and on the west partly by the approach way leading to the mosque`
  line `from the road leading from Garden Reach Road down to the river and partly by the Shah Munzil premises`
  line `together with the last mentioned approach way or passage passing through an op ening in the wall of the`
  line `Shah Munzil premises and leading on to the road running from Garden Reach Road to the river the length`
  line `of s uch way from the mosque being 72 feet.`
  line `IN WITNESS whereof the said parties to these presents have hereunto set their respective hands and`
  line `seals the day and year first above written.`
  line `Signed sealed and`
  line `delivered by the`
  line `above - named H. C. EGGAR.`
  line `Henry Cooper Eggar`
  line Seal.
