obj_root_law_sections_13_content:
  string
  line 13
  line `in the presence of`
  line `ERNEST H. COWIE.`
  line `Solicitor, Calcutta.`
  line `I 248 311`
  line `Presented for registration between the hours of 12 and 1 P.M., on the 7th day of February 1902, at the`
  line `Calcutta Registry office, by E.H. Cowie, of Calcutta, by occupation Solicitor, executant, as Attorney for`
  line `H.C. Eggar under a Power - of attorney authenticated by the Registrar of Calcutta on the 13th July 1900 and`
  line `rec orded as No. 193 for 1900.`
  line `E RNEST H. COWIE.`
  line `BEHARI LAL CHANDRA,`
  line Registrar.
  line `7 - 2 - 1902.`
  line `Execution was admitted by the aforesaid attorney under the power cited above who is personally known`
  line `to me.`
  line `ERNEST H. COWIE.`
  line `BEHARI LAL CHANDRA,`
  line Registrar.
  line `7 - 2 - 1902.`
  line `Registered in Book I.`
  line `Volume II.`
  line `Pages 131 to 136.`
  line `Being No. 248.`
  line `For 1902.`
  line `BEHARI LAL CHANDRA,`
  line `Registrar, Calcutta.`
  line `17 - 2 - 1902.`
  line ________
  line `The Seal`
  line `of the`
  line Registrar
  line of
  line Calcutta.
