obj_root_law_sections_21_content:
  string
  line 21
  line `The fourth Schedule above referred to.`
  line `P ART I.`
  line `Stock certificate standing in the name of the Comptroll er - General on account of the Sibtainabad`
  line `Emambarra Endowment Fund of the 3 ⅟ 2 per cent. loan of 1865 for R 4,00,000.`
  line `P ART I I.`
  line `Scale of estimated annual expenditure on the Emambarra and burial ground —`
  line R
  line `Pay of establishment at Emambarra`
  line `and burial ground.. 4,848`
  line `Pensions to retired servants.. 74`
  line `Lighting charges... 228`
  line `Petty expenses such as cost of s tationery and Manager’s gharry`
  line `hire on duty`
  line 72
  line `Repairs of the Emambarra.. 5, 965`
  line `Religious ceremonies... 3, 616`
  line `Allowance to Syed Saleh at Karbela 720`
  line `Contingencies including allowances to`
  line `clerical staff of the office of`
  line `Superintendent of Political`
  line `Pensions.... 477`
  line `T OTAL. Rs. 16,000`
  line `IN WITNES S whereof the said Prince Kumar Kader Mirza Abid Ali Bahadur, Prince Mirza Mahomed`
  line `Jalall, Prince Dilwar Jah Mirza, Prince Mirza Mahomed Askari and Prince Ibrahim Ali have hereunto set`
  line `their respective hands and seals this twenty - third day of November one thousand nine hundred and one.`
  line `Signed sealed and`
  line `delivered by the above -`
  line Seal.
