  line `Signed sealed and de - IBRAHIM ALI`
  line `livered by the above - MEERZA.`
  line `named Pri n ce Ibrahim`
  line `Ali in the presence of –`
  line `ERNEST H. COWIE.`
  line `P.67 281 16`
  line `Presented for Registration between the hours of 12 and 1 p.m., on the 7 th day of February 1902, at the`
  line `Calcutta Registry Office, by Prince Kumar Kader Mirza Mahomed Abid Ali, son of His Majesty the late`
  line `Wajid Ali Shah, of Kidderpore, by occupation pensioner, executant.`
